            "subheading": "Loyalty in Action",
            "title": "Be Loyal.",
            "heading_size": 100,
            "text": "<p>Black Lab is a small business with a big commitment to doing good. Our Be Loyal™ Program supports pets, people, and the planet through dog bed donations, sustainability-focused materials, and partnerships with causes we believe in. It’s how we turn values into action.</p>",
            "text_size": 100,
